    "updated_at": "2016-02-27T22:01:16Z",
    "body": "It looks like the idea of Nuts is to proxy file downloads from PRIVATE repos. Nuts server does not sit in your application but runs on it's own. Then your application's auto updater checks that server and downloads through it as a proxy. So it doesn't seem like you are using this for it's intended design. It isn't supposed to look for and fetch updates from itself.\n"
